Package info.smart_tools.smartactors.core.actors.annotations

  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    EntryPoint
    Annotation for handlers for which we should keep a context with the initial message.
    FromState
    Annotation for handlers which is accessible only from specific actor states.
    FromStates
    Wrapper annotation to support multiple FromState annotations.
    Handler
    Annotation for defining handler names for Actor methods.
    Handlers
    Wrapper annotation to support multiple Handler annotations.
    InitialState
    Annotation for defining initial state of the actor.
